sentences: Diamanté Anthony Blackmon (born January 3, 1991), better known by his stage name Carnage (or DJ Carnage), is a Guatemalan-American DJ and record producer.
Diamanté Anthony Blackmon was born on January 3, 1991, in Guatemala.
In October 2015, Carnage released his debut album Papi Gordo, which ranked at number 184 on the Billboard 200.
In April 2018, Carnage released his second album Battered Bruised & Bloody.
